<sect2>
<title>Installation of libgnome</title>

<para>Install libgnome by running the following commands:</para>

<para><screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/opt/gnome2 --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome --libexecdir=/opt/gnome2/sbin \
--with-gconf-source=xml::/etc/gnome/gconf/gconf.xml.defaults &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</userinput></screen></para>

</sect2>

